@commercial
title: Commercialize the Republican press
subtitle: We broaden our appeal, risking ideological clarity.
on-arrival: resources += 1; europe_relations += 1; conservative_strength += 4; moderate_strength += 2; liberal_strength += 2; radical_dissent += 5; middle_class_rep += 4; immigrant_laborers_rep += 3; rural_rep += 2; workers_rep += 1

Our newspapers shift toward patriotic business owners and loyal moderates. The party brings in more funds, but radicals decry the dilution of our Reconstruction values.

@campaign
title: Focus our press on campaigning
subtitle: Target loyal Republican voters and shore up our base.
