Election coverage strengthens enthusiasm among Republicans and mobilizes our base across the North and border states.

@ideological
title: Promote vibrant internal debate
subtitle: Let all factions express themselves through the press.
on-arrival: radical_dissent -= 5; moderate_dissent -= 5; conservative_dissent -= 5; liberal_dissent -= 5; workers_rep += 1; middle_class_rep += 1; freemen_rep += 1

We allow the party press to become a forum for ideas and factional debates. It risks some confusion in messaging, but tensions ease within the coalition.

