@Dixie

Using our media empire is eccential for reconstruction to counter the anti-freedmen and anti-reconstruction ideas in the south. But to which state will we target in this cycle?

- @DeepSouth: Alabama, Mississippi, Georgia, Florida
- @Carolinas: North and South Carolina
- @MississippiValley: Louisiana and Arkansas 
- @Texas: TEXAS

